CustomField.description: Defines the default Team Member permission level for roles accessing the Manage Team and Team Schedule Management pages. Valid values are integers where 0 is None (no access), 1 is Read, and 2 is Edit. If not defined, the default is 1 (Read).
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines the default Team Member permission level for roles accessing the Manage Team and Team Schedule Management pages. Valid values are integers where 0 is None (no access), 1 is Read, and 2 is Edit. If not defined, the default is 1 (Read).
CustomField.label: Team Member Permission Level
